title: Harry and order of phoenix
description: Welcome to the unofficial guide to, in my opinion, the best game from the Harry Potter series so far: Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix. The guide is divided into two big parts: the encyclopedia and the walkthrough. In encyclopedia you will find detailed information which help you to achieve 100% in game stats.
